 // |      |      |      |      |      |      |                      |      |      |      |      |      |      |
 // |      |      |      |      |      |      |                      |      |      |      |      |      |      |
 // |      |      |      |      |      |      |                      |      |      |      |      |      |      |
 // |      |      |      |      |      |      |      |        |      |      |      |      |      |      |      |
 // |      |      |      |      |      |      |      |        |      |      |      |      |      |      |      |
                     bindings = <
     &trans  &trans     &trans    &trans     &trans     &trans                               &trans  &trans     &trans     &trans    &trans       &trans
     &trans  &kp LBRC   &kp AMPS  &kp STAR   &kp LPAR   &kp RBRC                             &trans  &trans     &trans     &trans    &bootloader  &trans
     &trans  &kp COLON  &kp DLLR  &kp PRCNT  &kp CARET  &kp PLUS                             &trans  &kp RSHFT  &kp RCTRL  &kp RALT  &kp RGUI     &trans
     &trans  &kp TILDE  &kp EXCL  &kp AT     &kp POUND  &kp PIPE  &trans             &trans  &trans  &trans     &trans     &kp LALT  &trans       &trans
     &trans  &trans     &trans    &trans     &kp LPAR   &kp RPAR  &kp UNDER          &trans  &trans  &trans     &trans     &trans    &trans       &trans
                     >;
